Key metrics

Generative Affordance Score
How many coherent futures remain possible?

Directional Bias
How strongly the prompt points toward one class of answer.

Entropy Decay Rate
How fast the response collapses from many futures to one path.

Trajectory Stability
How well the answer stays in one basin without wobble.

Distortion Cost
What got lost by choosing this frame.

Counterfactual Sensitivity
What small prompt changes would have produced a different path.

⸻

Failure modes
	•	False lock: commits too early to wrong interpretation
	•	Over-broad basin: answer becomes mushy and vague
	•	Over-tight lock: answer becomes brittle and too literal
	•	Ghost trajectory bleed: philosophy leaks into technical answer, or vice versa
	•	Constraint inversion: style or helpfulness overwhelms accuracy
	•	Narrative hijack: story-form dominates when analysis was needed

